title: [Hamioukatou's General Store]
[Hamioukatou's Weaponry]
description: Textured black silk walls rise from a polished oak floor.  Just above a large potted fern hangs a tasteful rune staff display, and a sturdy oak beam ceiling completes the picture.  An engraved pine case and a large cherrywood cabinet stand side by side in the middle of the room.
